@startuml
title LowCortisol Platform - IAM Backend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "IAM Backend Bounded Context" {
  class "Application" as Backend_iam_Application <<layer>>
  class "Domain" as Backend_iam_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Backend_iam_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Interfaces REST" as Backend_iam_Interfaces_REST <<layer>>
}

Backend_iam_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_iam_Application : commands / queries
Backend_iam_Application ..> Backend_iam_Domain : model and policies
Backend_iam_Application ..> Backend_iam_Infrastructure : repository ports / adapters
Backend_iam_Infrastructure ..> Backend_iam_Domain : persistence mapping
Backend_iam_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_iam_Domain : resources from aggregates

note bottom of Backend_iam_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/backend/layers/iam.
end note

@enduml
